## S8086d9-1 Implementation Log

Date: 2026-07-07
Story: サイドバー 物理/スマート ビュー切替 + スマートフォルダ描画

### Files Changed

- packages/ui/src/api.ts
  - Added imports: smartViewConfigSchema, smartFoldersResolveResponseSchema, SmartViewConfig, SmartFoldersResolveResponse
  - Added api.listSmartFolders() → GET /api/smart-folders
  - Added api.resolveSmartFolder(id) → GET /api/smart-folders/{id}/notes

- packages/ui/src/components/SmartView.tsx (new)
