  - SmartFolder (query kind): collapsible, lazy-resolves notes on first expand
  - SmartPin (pin kind): leaf node, click navigates to note
  - SmartIcon: built-in name→SVG map (12 icons) + emoji/unknown passthrough; always sets data-icon

- packages/ui/src/App.tsx
  - Added sidebarView state ('physical'|'smart') persisted to localStorage('loamium.sidebarView')
  - Added switchSidebarView callback
  - Added sidebar-view-physical / sidebar-view-smart toggle buttons (aria-pressed)
  - Conditionally renders SmartView or FileTree in sidebar

- packages/ui/src/styles.css
  - Added .sidebar-view-toggle / .sidebar-view-btn styles for toggle
  - Added .smart-view / .smart-view-state / .smart-folder-* / .smart-note-item / .smart-pin-btn / .smart-icon styles

### Key Design Decisions

- data-testid="smart-folder" placed on wrapper div (not inner button) so that smart-folder-error is a descendant of smart-folder (required for test locator chaining)
- icon fallback: icon field absent → kind default (pin→'file-text', query→'search'); data-icon always set to raw icon string (even defaults)
- SmartFolder fetches notes only on first expand (idle→loading→loaded/error); re-expand after error is kept as-is (no re-fetch)

